{"tid":2116004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫情擴散    滙豐及集友銀行明起縮短營業時間","createTime":"2020-07-20T01:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T01:29:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"02608f83efb77d4fb4eb1c3fd04a711443051d50","tid":2116004,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hnFn5fM2bZKBEJcOZmhQ2Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/1891337748be56b242f6cca48eb9ca93\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhnFn5fM2bZKBEJcOZmhQ2Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F1891337748be56b242f6cca48eb9ca93&h=2bf1fd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為減低新冠病毒疫情擴散，有銀行調整營業時間。其中滙豐銀行明天(20日)起，全線分行周一至周五營業時間改為上午9時至下午4時，周六營業時間維持不變，繼續至下午1時。<br />\n<br />\n此外，滙豐旗下3部流動銀行，及2間位於觀塘及上水的中小企中心，分別由明天和後天(21日)起暫停服務，直至另行通知。滙豐早前已暫時關閉3間位於機場、土瓜灣和水泉澳邨的零售銀行分行，及1間位於沙田的中小企中心。<br />\n<br />\n另外，集友銀行全線分行亦由明天起，周一至周五營業時間至下午3時，周六則至中午12時。其中慈雲山分行明日起暫停服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/新冠疫情擴散-滙豐及集友銀行明起縮短營業時間-143356627.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%93%B4%E6%95%A3-%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E5%8F%8A%E9%9B%86%E5%8F%8B%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E7%B8%AE%E7%9F%AD%E7%87%9F%E6%A5%AD%E6%99%82%E9%96%93-143356627.html&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=d92a31bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/新冠疫情擴散-滙豐及集友銀行明起縮短營業時間-143356627.html</a>"}]}